{"tid":2177940,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：把數百萬人次分拆7日141個地點 不可與選舉直接比較","createTime":"2020-08-28T05:17:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T06:15:22.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9e7b0476c8ca7573d9a338dc1b10ad88e1545015","tid":2177940,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T05:17:25.000Z","msg":"聶德權：檢測計劃人群聚集情況與選舉不可比較<br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局長聶德權被問到，「普及社區檢測計劃」可做到感染控制，為何不能在立法會選舉時做到，他表示，選舉不只是一天的投票日，亦包括選前期活動等，政府經評估後認為在疫情期間，首要是做好抗疫工作，並不適宜舉行選舉。<br />\n<br />\n他指，檢測人數聚集，與選舉一日之內有大量人士投票是不同，認為兩者差別大，不可作比較。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2354637\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2354637&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONgxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=fcdad4f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2354637</a>"},{"pid":"ab9f8e2fd2e2439ba7813ab8dbbf24cc7512fe54","tid":2177940,"uid":21470,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T05:17:57.000Z","msg":"每日百萬人次返工又點計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"42b3092471da42d700c834e28e1b4a8fbf1fa52f","tid":2177940,"uid":28641,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T05:19:04.000Z","msg":"當你知道自己9Up但啲市民反抗嘅方法就係講一句<br />\n屌你老母死全家時<br />\n唔好話9Up啦<br />\n是但講完用google translate播返出來都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c975fe7aef01f6a4e38e938d8b341cbe4b2e628","tid":2177940,"uid":178875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab9f8e2fd2e2439ba7813ab8dbbf24cc7512fe54","tid":2177940,"uid":21470,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T05:17:57.000Z","msg":"每日百萬人次返工又點計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T05:19:27.000Z","msg":"陳婆婆:唔係個個WFH咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66871c995c45d40a19d69c6df11a78ea7d16cc8